572
00:34:13,468 --> 00:34:13,988
Let's go.

573
00:34:14,268 --> 00:34:14,868
Then we'll leave.

574
00:34:15,268 --> 00:34:16,448
Just go.

575
00:34:16,948 --> 00:34:17,627
Bye.

576
00:34:49,548 --> 00:34:50,748
Well,

577
00:34:52,308 --> 00:34:54,187
