581
00:35:09,268 --> 00:35:10,388
Let's be realistic.

582
00:35:10,948 --> 00:35:12,268
Given Lin Tuo's current situation,

583
00:35:13,588 --> 00:35:15,108
if he wants to do something silly

584
00:35:15,468 --> 00:35:16,068
like that,

585
00:35:16,788 --> 00:35:17,828
