616
00:36:20,588 --> 00:36:21,868
I'd be surprised if you get a wife.

617
00:36:22,188 --> 00:36:25,508
I-It runs in my family.

618
00:36:25,748 --> 00:36:27,068
My dad snores too.

619
00:36:27,068 --> 00:36:29,308
