736
00:42:23,508 --> 00:42:24,188
Don't worry.

737
00:42:24,868 --> 00:42:26,828
We never run away.

738
00:42:27,508 --> 00:42:27,948
Okay.

739
00:42:28,788 --> 00:42:30,308
